{"tid":2263974,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係藍波撚的表哥","createTime":"2020-10-30T09:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T09:41:57.000Z","uid":366192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7476cfb3f5c6f11380da51b129f1aaff447ab49a","tid":2263974,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"唔好怪藍波撚啦 其實佢地全部都仲係小學生黎<br />\n我係佢地嘅表哥 唔係好親個隻<br />\n佢地有少少低智個d唔好講啦<br />\n佢地讀特殊學校個d都無謂提<br />\n不過大家放過佢地啦 佢地仲係讀緊小三<br />\n佢地老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧藍波撚<br />\n佢地出街已經會跳起身扮射波 踢拖著埋長襪<br />\n我代佢地喺呢度向大家道歉一聲"},{"pid":"e135e744996d8d4db746027d42ceb9c4b691dd1c","tid":2263974,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"有冇新意"},{"pid":"6a9e5918644404ee66e83238ca599a9a7cb21583","tid":2263974,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"真，d 中學雞行行下無lala 跳起扮射波，真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7854031d7b534f9802160a05ce40a56bcab0e47","tid":2263974,"uid":366192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e135e744996d8d4db746027d42ceb9c4b691dd1c","tid":2263974,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"有冇新意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"不及藍波撚有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0wgwEF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0wgwEF.gif&h=7534c1f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f78cb5839c9250f3da3ef68ac0a0ee6ada0cd8d","tid":2263974,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"表弟你做咩咁曳呀"},{"pid":"3667f1ed1ef620ddea76d8ce1c44ef56341cbd54","tid":2263974,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f78cb5839c9250f3da3ef68ac0a0ee6ada0cd8d","tid":2263974,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30